>If I had to guess, I'd say there is a small difference, and that's the
>interior light, in a passenger bus, there's two interior lights(I'm 
>assuming
>it's the same on a bay as on a split), whereas there's only one on a single
>cab.  The remedy for this would be to just cut the wire for the second
>interior light off of the harness.  That's the only difference that I know
>of.  Good luck with the wiring.
